<b>2013 April 20 - 21&nbsp;&nbsp;   Yoko Okamoto Sensei, 6th dan, in Manila and Cebu</b><br><br><br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
<img src="../photos/photos/WEBokamoto.jpg" style="padding:2px; margin:2px; border: 0px solid ; width: 491px; height: 650px;"  vspace="2" alt="Okamoto"></a><br>

Yoko Okamoto Sensei, 6th dan, will conduct a seminar in Manila on April 20, and in Cebu City the following day.<br><br> 

Okamoto Sensei is one of the highest-ranking women in the world of aikido. She has dojos in Kyoto and Portland, Oregon.<br><br>

Those wishing to purchase early bird tickets can pay to any officer of the Makati Aikido Club before the deadline. See poster for details.

